title: Some of my pictures have disappeared from my Google Pixel 3A XL
content: After I woke up today I saw that A LOT of my images had disappeared from my Gallery Go and Google photos I do not have smart storage turned on and I have no idea why some of the images are there and the rest are gone. These are really important images and precious memories if anybody can please offer some help or insight  let me know.  I have the folders still there but there is significantly less photos and I can't find them anywhere please help.
